        <definition>virtual bool endstone::DamageSource::isIndirect</definition>
        <argsstring>() const =0</argsstring>
        <name>isIndirect</name>
        <qualifiedname>endstone::DamageSource::isIndirect</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Get if this damage is indirect. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Damage is considered indirect if <ref refid="classendstone_1_1DamageSource_1a4db47c0262336513f37cb47c7bac0b73" kindref="member">DamageSource::getActor()</ref> is not equal to <ref refid="classendstone_1_1DamageSource_1aaffa76098f44b6d00d74775316c05139" kindref="member">DamageSource::getDamagingActor()</ref>. This will be the case, for example, if a skeleton shot an arrow or a player threw a potion.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para><computeroutput>true</computeroutput> if is indirect, <computeroutput>false</computeroutput> otherwise. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
